description: A decorated Army veteran likely suffering from post-traumatic stress disorder called U.S. government leadership "weak" and appeared to acknowledge he purposely blew up a Tesla Cybertruck at the entrance of Trump International Hotel in Las Vegas on New Year's Day, police said Friday.
